column5: Never did get this photo posting thingie.....here goes. If everything works well you should see a photo of my best buddy Benson...
WTG John, good lookin pooch too
Should get him to meet Marvin........
They'd probably be instand friends John, Marvin's never met another dog he didn't like.
Ben too Lew, however he did meet a boxer one time who decided to get a little amorous, Ben wasn't too happy as they hadn't even been introduced...
nice shot of Ben there John  now...  how about some fishing photos?
My wife would love your 'best bud'.    Ok, now that you posted a pic, what others you got for us ?
Nice pic! Good work on posting that first photo.
Congrats on posting your first pic! Now let's see some big fish...caught in warm weather....ahh summer time....
Not a biggie, but this was last year's pike tourny at Lakair....
Nice little pike there!  My wife and I are heading up to Lakair for the OFC weekend for the first time this year.  Cant wait...thanks for the pic!
